title: 2020 Week 7: Giants-Eagles TNF Recap
itunes:title: 2020 Week 7: Giants-Eagles TNF Recap
description:
Gregg Rosenthal is joined by USA Today's Steven Ruiz to talk about the race for NFC East. Danny Dimes had a run for the ages, but it wasn't enough and the Eagles snuck out the win.
